HEADWORD: Siluroid
<hw>Si*lu"roid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Silurus</ets>
+ <ets>-oid</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Belonging to the
